Class Summary 
Class Description
AddressBook
Address Book Library This address book library can be used to create a new address book and store/modify/delete entries with values like Name, Postal Address, Phone Number, Email Address, Notes.
AddressBook.AddressBookEntry
AddressBookEntry This class stores the values associated with each Address book entry added.
AddressBook.AddressBookEntry.PostalAddress
PostalAddress This class store the postal address associated with each Address book entry added.
